    "description": "Are you a skilled Senior Software Engineer looking for your next big career move? Mindtree in Dhanbad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Mindtree:\nMindtree is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Rust\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mindtree!",
